环境配置：需要在HDFS HA搭建的前提下，搭建yarn
注意端口的开放：8088（node07 node08，用途：网页访问）,8033（node06,node07,node08;作用resourceManager 访问nodeManager,）
1. 在node05(管理节点)配置基本信息 
 Configure parameters as follows:
    1.1 etc/hadoop/mapred-site.xml(可复制mapred-site.xml.template):

    <property>
        <name>mapreduce.framework.name</name>
        <value>yarn</value>
    </property>


    1.2 etc/hadoop/yarn-site.xml:
    
    <property>
        <name>yarn.nodemanager.aux-services</name>
        <value>mapreduce_shuffle</value>
    </property>
     <property>
        <name>yarn.resourcemanager.ha.enabled</name>
        <value>true</value>
    </property>
    <property>
        <name>yarn.resourcemanager.cluster-id</name>
        <value>cluster1</value>
    </property>
    <property>
        <name>yarn.resourcemanager.ha.rm-ids</name>
        <value>rm1,rm2</value>
    </property>
    <property>
        <name>yarn.resourcemanager.hostname.rm1</name>
        <value>node07</value>
    </property>
    <property>
        <name>yarn.resourcemanager.hostname.rm2</name>
        <value>node08</value>
    </property>
    <property>
        <name>yarn.resourcemanager.zk-address</name>
        <value>node06:2181,node07:2181,node08:2181</value>
    </property>
    
2. 将node05配置的mapred-site.xml、yarn-site.xml分发给其他节点
    # scp yarn-site.xml mapred-site.xml node06:`pwd`
    # scp yarn-site.xml mapred-site.xml node07:`pwd`
    # scp yarn-site.xml mapred-site.xml node08:`pwd`
3. 启动ResourceManager
    3.1 在node05 使用启动脚本启动：
        # start-yarn.sh 
        starting yarn daemons
        starting resourcemanager, logging to /opt/sxt/hadoop-2.6.5/logs/yarn-root-resourcemanager-node05.out
        node08: starting nodemanager, logging to /opt/sxt/hadoop-2.6.5/logs/yarn-root-nodemanager-node08.out
        node07: starting nodemanager, logging to /opt/sxt/hadoop-2.6.5/logs/yarn-root-nodemanager-node07.out
        node06: starting nodemanager, logging to /opt/sxt/hadoop-2.6.5/logs/yarn-root-nodemanager-node06.out
        可以看见：nodemanager启动了，但是node07、node08的resourcemanager没有启动

    3.2 在node07、node08启动 resourcemanager
    # yarn-daemon.sh start resourcemanager
    starting resourcemanager, logging to /opt/sxt/hadoop-2.6.5/logs/yarn-root-resourcemanager-node07.out
    # yarn-daemon.sh start resourcemanager
    starting resourcemanager, logging to /opt/sxt/hadoop-2.6.5/logs/yarn-root-resourcemanager-node08.out
    注：可用jps产看到 resourcemanager 这个角色

4. 测试MapReduce
    4.1 进入下面这个目录
      # cd /opt/sxt/hadoop-2.6.5/share/hadoop/mapreduce
    4.2 执行下面这个命令，计算
    # hadoop jar hadoop-mapreduce-examples-2.6.5.jar wordcount /user/root/practice.txt /data/wc/output_005
